---
import Layout from '@/components/chrome/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — The STR Ledger"
  description="Privacy policy for thestrledger.com. How we handle the data the site collects."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <section class="bg-parchment">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-12 pb-9">
      <p class="label text-gold-deep">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-serif text-h1 text-navy leading-tight">
        Privacy Policy<span class="period-gold">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lead text-ink-2">
        The short version: thestrledger.com is a static catalog site. No user accounts, no databases of customer data living on our servers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-parchment-light border-t border-rule">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-9 prose">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-navy">What we collect</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-ink-2 leading-snug">
        Standard server logs (IP, user-agent, timestamp). If you submit the email-capture form for the free 47-deductions PDF or buy a workbook, we store the email address you provide for fulfillment and our operator newsletter.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-7 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Analytics</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-ink-2 leading-snug">
        We may use Google Analytics 4 for traffic measurement. GA4 sets cookies in your browser per Google's policies.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-7 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Payments</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-ink-2 leading-snug">
        Workbook purchases are processed by our payment provider (Stripe or equivalent). We never see your full card number; the provider tokenizes payment data per their PCI policies.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-7 font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Email</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body text-ink-2 leading-snug">
        We do not sell your email address. Every newsletter has an unsubscribe link. Request deletion at <a href="mailto:hello@thestrledger.com" class="font-mono">hello@thestrledger.com</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-7 text-caption text-ink-3 italic">
        This stub is a placeholder. See <a href="/terms/" class="text-navy">Terms</a> and <a href="/disclosures/" class="text-navy">Disclosures</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
